,[318,3221]]},{"text":"能完成的。”","box":[[312,3281],[766,3269],[768,3354],[315,3366]]},{"text":"一《论联合政府》（一九四五年四月二","box":[[787,3282],[2178,3282],[2178,3348],[787,3348]]},{"text":"180","box":[[384,3465],[497,3465],[497,3530],[384,3530]]}],"dimensions":{"height":3823,"width":2603}}